commits.subject: FIRST CRACK AT RT PLAN (WIP ONLY) - Removed the Prescription Dose section from DoseControlPanel and replaced it with a new RadiationTherapyPanel for combined dose and plan visualization. - Updated ViewerInterface to handle RT Plan series, including state management for selected plans and beams. - Enhanced WorkingViewer to render beam overlays, improving visualization of treatment plans. - Registered new RT Plan API routes in the server for handling plan data. - Adjusted UI components for better responsiveness and user interaction with RT data.
commits.regulatoryDescription: ENHANCEMENT: Initial implementation AT RT PLAN (Work in progress) - Removed the Prescription Dose section from DoseControlPanel and replaced it with a new RadiationTherapyPanel for combined dose and plan visualization. - Updated ViewerInterface to handle RT Plan series, including state management for selected plans and beams. - Enhanced WorkingViewer to render beam overlays, improving visualization of treatment plans. - Registered new RT Plan API routes in the server for handling plan data. - Adjusted UI components for better responsiveness and user interaction with RT data [RT Plan, Image Viewing, User Interface, Data Management, Infrastructure]
